2 Days Ago Biden currently has at least 253 electoral votes. The magic number is 270. If he wins Pennsylvania — a state won by Trump in 2016 — and its 20 electoral votes, he would pass that threshold. US networks have said so far the race wass still too close to call. Biden is also currently in the lead in key states including Arizona, Georgia and Nevada. Fox News and the Associated Press have already called Arizona in Biden’s favour but other US media have said the race is still too close to call. Trump has amassed 214 electoral votes so far, with his path to victory narrowing. The Republican incumbent has made unsubstantiated claims of massive voter fraud.